plot: JJ falls for Lara, who works in the sweet shop with him, but when he visits her flat, he discovers that she is a single parent with a baby, Albert. JJ's family disapproves of Lara as being a tart, and Emily tells him she thinks Lara is using him to get back at her violent ex-boyfriend Liam. JJ gets into a fight with Liam, who tells him that he loves his child and gives JJ his blessing if he will care for Lara. JJ gets back together with Lara and serenades her on the ukulele.—don @ minifie-1
